What you need to know:

Rowland was also using more than USD1 million every year to hire mercenaries to guard his militarised farms.Some people even thought Tiny Rowland got away with his corrupt dealings because Lonrho was a British intelligence front.Moi sent Bethuel Kiplagat to Gorongosa to meet Renamo leader Afonso Dhalakama.Kiplagat had to find his way through the Gorongosa bush to look for Dhlakama’s hideout. 